.modal-header
  h6.modal-title.text-center Approve Process Service Plan
.modal-body
  .alert.alert-description
    | Once you approve the selected service plan, you won't be able to make further changes to the current process model.
    br 
    | If you want to make further changes, you will have to create a new version based on current process model.
.modal-footer
  .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2.text-center
    .col-md-6
      button.btn.btn-sm.btn-block.btn-success(type="button" ng-click="$close('yes')")
        | Yes, approve it
        i.fa.fa-check.margin-l--soft
    .col-md-6
      button.btn.btn-sm.btn-block.btn-warning(ng-click="$dismiss()")
        | Cancel
        i.fa.fa-ban.margin-l--soft
